<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />But God will shoot them;</para>

<para style="q1">suddenly they will be wounded with his arrows.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />They will be made to stumble, since their own tongues are against them;</para>

<para style="q1">all who see them will wag their heads.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />All people will fear</para>

<para style="q1">and will declare God's deeds.</para>

<para style="q1">They will wisely think about what he has done.</para>
